# Password recovery reveals wheter an email is registered

Precondition:
- User is on the password recovery page

Steps:
- Navigate to login
- Click "Forgot your password?"
- Enter a registered email adress
- Submit the request
- Repeat the process using an unregistered email adress

Expected result:
- The system should display a generic response regardless of wheter the email exists or not


Source: https://mega.nz/recovery
